attributes.description: This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of threat intelligence events detected in the user's environment using GreyNoise data.

params.markdown:
**Threat Intelligence** | [Threat Feed Overview](#/dashboard/ti_greynoise-24d2c409-0abf-415a-aa3d-a6d007c42ba3)

This dashboard provides a comprehensive view of threat intelligence events detected using GreyNoise data. It delivers insights into event distribution, threat analysis, and categorized breakdowns by classification.

Key metrics include total detected events, unique IPs detected. Detected events are further analyzed by classification types, country, tags, business service category, and actors to identify patterns.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/ti_greynoise/overview)
